{#
@file
The template for the default teaser.

If a cotnent type is missing a template, this template will be used as a fallback.

Available variables:
- type: The type of card. Either 'card' or 'story'.
- image: The Image object.
  - url: The image URL.
  - alt: The image alt text.
- favorite: Boolean. Whether or not to show the favorites icon.
- title: The title.
- content: The content.
- button: Array of button objects.
  - url: The button URL.
  - color: The button color.
  - text: The button text.
- link: Array of link objects.
  - url: The link URL.
  - text: The link text.
- tags: Array of tag objects.
  - type: The tag type. Either 'alt' or 'standard'.
  - background: The tag background color.
  - data: Array of tag objects.
#}

{% set data = {
  'title': node.title.value,
  'content': node.field_description.value|default(content.body),
  'button': {
    'url': node|entity_url,
    'color': 'maroon',
    'text': 'View',
  },
  'favorite': true
} %}

<article class="node__teaser">
  {{ include('@analytics/teaser.html.twig', data) }}
</article>
